parameters.text:
=You are Techdome‚Äôs AI DevOps assistant.
Analyze this Jira issue update and assign a risk level (Low, Medium, High) with a short reasoning.

Here‚Äôs the issue data in JSON:
{{ JSON.stringify($json) }}

Return the response only in this JSON format:
{
  "risk_level": "",
  "impact_summary": ""
}

parameters.jsCode:
return items.map(item => {
  try {
    const parsed = JSON.parse(item.json.output.replace(/```json|```/g, "").trim());
    return {
      json: {
        ...item.json,
        risk_level: parsed.risk_level,
        impact_summary: parsed.impact_summary
      }
    };
  } catch (error) {
    return {
      json: {
        ...item.json,
        risk_level: "Unknown",
        impact_summary: "Failed to parse AI output"
      }
    };
  }
});
